FBIS4-45587 "jptdd028__l94087" JPRS-TDD-94-028-L JPRS Narcotics 23 June 1994 WEST EUROPE AUSTRIA Former Player for Spanish Soccer Club Caught Carrying 4.5 Kg Former Player for Spanish Soccer Club Caught Carrying 4.5 Kg of Cocaine AU2306172894 Vienna NEUE KRONEN-ZEITUNG in German 23 Jun 94 p 11 AU2306172894 Vienna NEUE KRONEN-ZEITUNG German BFN [Severin Corti report: "Former Soccer Star as Drug Smuggler"] [Excerpt] First, the customs officials at Vienna's Schwechat airport were surprised about the strange flight route: The Spaniard Hugo Mezna Benitez, former player for the FC Barcelona soccer club, had traveled to Vienna from Barcelona via Bogota. Then the investigators discovered that they had caught a big fish: The former soccer player carried 4.5 kg of cocaine worth 15 million schillings. [passage omitted]
